what do I do now?

42
00:02:54,740 --> 00:02:57,230
You shitty father... I mean, Father.

43
00:02:57,230 --> 00:03:00,620
You didn't even hesitate that time!
I felt that malice!

44
00:03:00,620 --> 00:03:03,300
I feel your anger, my son!

45
00:03:03,300 --> 00:03:05,190
I will not accept this!

46
00:03:05,190 --> 00:03:08,420
Who is this fiend who took
my dearest brother's position?

47
00:03:08,420 --> 00:03:09,890
I will go talk to them personally!

48
00:03:09,890 --> 00:03:15,250
Alice, I appreciate it, but we're
talking about the son of a viscount.

49
00:03:15,250 --> 00:03:16,210
Uh-huh! Uh-huh!

50
00:03:17,240 --> 00:03:20,280
But... that's simply not fair,
my dear brother!

51
00:03:20,830 --> 00:03:25,640
I know! Why not take the exam
for the Hero Academy?

52
00:03:25,920 --> 00:03:28,020
The Hero Academy, eh?

53
00:03:28,470 --> 00:03:33,610
Those who graduate from the Hero Academy
can become monster hunters or royal knights.

54
00:03:33,610 --> 00:03:37,180
Basically, you're set for life if you make it there.

55
00:03:38,710 --> 00:03:40,640
