233
00:13:14,830 --> 00:13:16,770
I-I beat it...

234
00:13:17,510 --> 00:13:19,610
But I'm kinda tired now.

235
00:13:20,370 --> 00:13:24,420
I'm going to have to figure out how
to rake in that LP from now on.

236
00:13:24,950 --> 00:13:27,610
