238
00:13:33,860 --> 00:13:38,670
Is my lap a comferble...
a comfortable pillow for you?

239
00:13:38,670 --> 00:13:41,420
Man, I feel alive again.

240
00:13:41,910 --> 00:13:44,230
Can I get a goodnight hug, too?

241
00:13:44,230 --> 00:13:45,010
Huh?!

242
00:13:45,900 --> 00:13:50,380
I'm so blessed to have such
a cute, kind little sister!

243
00:13:50,470 --> 00:13:52,930
Noir Stardia

244
00:13:54,200 --> 00:13:56,440
The Hidden Dungeon Only I Can Enter.

245
00:14:01,640 --> 00:14:03,880
Sorry to keep you waiting, Noir.

246
00:14:05,150 --> 00:14:08,640
S-Sorry to call you out of the blue.

247
00:14:08,640 --> 00:14:11,140
No, it's fine. What did
you want to talk about?

248
00:14:11,140 --> 00:14:12,820
I have a favor to ask.

249
00:14:13,140 --> 00:14:15,970
Also, you seem a bit different today.

250
00:14:15,970 --> 00:14:18,310
Y-You think so?

251
00:14:18,310 --> 00:14:20,840
You're usually more reserved.

252
00:14:20,840 --> 00:14:23,490
Well, everyone's always staring at my chest!

253
00:14:23,490 --> 00:14:25,170
Of course I'd want to hide it.

254
00:14:25,830 --> 00:14:28,050
I'm not sure if that outfit is helping...

255
00:14:28,050 --> 00:14:30,860
Well, that's because today's
supposed to be special!

256
00:14:30,860 --> 00:14:32,280
Noir, you doofus.

257
00:14:32,280 --> 00:14:34,330
Sorry! I was just worried.

258
00:14:34,330 --> 00:14:36,950
I've known you forever,
and you're important to me.

259
00:14:36,950 --> 00:14:40,190
Just saying that I'm important
to you isn't enough!

260
00:14:40,190 --> 00:14:43,150
Th-Then... can I hug you?

261
00:14:44,110 --> 00:14:45,610
Sure...

262
00:14:47,840 --> 00:14:50,360
Okay... here I go.

263
00:14:51,990 --> 00:14:55,190
Your scent is so calming.

264
00:14:55,190 --> 00:14:56,660
Not to mention...

265
00:14:56,660 --> 00:14:58,660
Noir Stardia

266
00:14:58,870 --> 00:15:01,420
A few hours prior

267
00:15:01,710 --> 00:15:03,830
So, Olivia...

268
00:15:03,830 --> 00:15:05,200
You hear somethin'?

269
00:15:05,880 --> 00:15:07,840
M-Master...

270
00:15:07,840 --> 00:15:09,050
Yes?

271
00:15:09,050 --> 00:15:12,000
I was hoping I could make
a skill that would help me

272
00:15:12,000 --> 00:15:13,930
with the Hero Academy exam.

273
00:15:13,930 --> 00:15:16,090
This calls for cheating!

274
00:15:16,090 --> 00:15:17,560
You're awful, you know that?

275
00:15:17,560 --> 00:15:19,870
And you're too much of a goody two shoes.

276
00:15:19,870 --> 00:15:22,460
That's exactly why they took your job.

277
00:15:23,520 --> 00:15:27,610
It takes 300 LP to use,
but I've got just the skill for you.

278
00:15:27,610 --> 00:15:28,900
You interested?

279
00:15:28,900 --> 00:15:30,280
Yes, please!

280
00:15:30,650 --> 00:15:32,280
In that case...

281
00:15:32,610 --> 00:15:40,160
Discerning Eye

282
00:15:32,610 --> 00:15:40,160
Have a peek into
information about any
living creature or object.

283
00:15:32,960 --> 00:15:35,180
The skill that grants you a peek
into any kind of information:

284
00:15:35,180 --> 00:15:37,010
The Discerning Eye!

285
00:15:37,010 --> 00:15:40,290
With this, you're good to go on your exam!

286
00:15:40,820 --> 00:15:42,500
Thanks, Emma.

287
00:15:42,500 --> 00:15:45,630
It's fine. This is basically a greeting.

288
00:15:45,990 --> 00:15:49,230
Okay, now to Get Creative and
create the Discerning Eye skill.

289
00:15:49,170 --> 00:15:50,550
Noir Stardia  LP.950

290
00:15:49,170 --> 00:15:52,130
Skills [Great Sage]
Skill \h[Get Creative] [Editor] [Bestow]
Skill \h[LP Conversion] [Stone Bullet]
Skill \h[Discerning Eye]

291
00:15:49,170 --> 00:15:52,130
Noir Stardia  LP.650

292
00:15:53,350 --> 00:15:54,970
Let's try it out.

293
00:15:56,550 --> 00:16:03,270
Emma Brightness  Lv.17

294
00:15:56,550 --> 00:16:03,270
Species
Occupation
Skills

295
00:15:57,010 --> 00:16:03,270
[Human]
[Librarian]
[Dual-Wielded Daggers (Grade C)]
[Wind Strike]

296
00:15:57,130 --> 00:15:58,180
I see it!

297
00:15:58,180 --> 00:16:00,600
This means I'll pass for sure!

298
00:16:00,600 --> 00:16:02,670
I need to make sure I thank Emma properly.

299
00:16:03,450 --> 00:16:06,220
Man, my shoulders are so stiff.

300
00:16:06,220 --> 00:16:07,730
My chest is way too heavy.

301
00:16:08,210 --> 00:16:09,070
All right!

302
00:16:09,070 --> 00:16:15,070
Skill

303
00:16:09,070 --> 00:16:15,070
Small Boobs

304
00:16:09,330 --> 00:16:12,030
I'll use Get Creative and
give Emma Small Boobs.

305
00:16:12,030 --> 00:16:15,060
I'll need a total of 80 LP to do this, but...

306
00:16:12,070 --> 00:16:15,070
Needed to Get Creative          LP.30
Needed to Bestow to Emma  LP.50

307
00:16:15,410 --> 00:16:16,310
There!

308
00:16:27,000 --> 00:16:29,710
Wh-What just happened?!

309
00:16:29,710 --> 00:16:32,320
Wh-What? Why?!

310
00:16:32,320 --> 00:16:35,000
Now your shoulders won't be so stiff.

311
00:16:35,000 --> 00:16:37,810
Don't worry, plenty of people
love small boobs. Isn't that great?

312
00:16:37,810 --> 00:16:39,350
Are you being serious right now?

313
00:16:39,350 --> 00:16:40,250
Yup!

314
00:16:40,250 --> 00:16:42,430
Though I definitely prefer them big.

315
00:16:42,430 --> 00:16:46,190
Gimme back my boobs, you doofus!

316
00:16:46,680 --> 00:16:49,560
I ended up having to use Editor
to give her boobs back.

317
00:16:50,000 --> 00:16:51,940
Talk about a waste of LP.

318
00:16:52,740 --> 00:16:54,950
Hero Academy        The Day of the Exam

319
00:16:55,250 --> 00:16:56,280
Feeling confident?

320
00:16:56,280 --> 00:16:57,530
But of course.

321
00:16:57,530 --> 00:16:59,480
Barons and viscounts...

322
00:16:59,480 --> 00:17:02,910
They're totally different
from a baronet like me.

323
00:17:03,500 --> 00:17:06,040
We will now begin the entrance exam.

324
00:17:06,400 --> 00:17:09,330
Your task is to collect raw
materials from monsters.

325
00:17:09,330 --> 00:17:12,300
You'll be judged on how much you bring
in and how rare the materials are.

326
00:17:12,300 --> 00:17:16,430
This will be a team effort in which
you split up into groups of three.

327
00:17:16,800 --> 00:17:18,920
Return empty-handed, and you fail!

328
00:17:18,920 --> 00:17:19,800
That is all!

329
00:17:19,800 --> 00:17:21,200
We have to make a team?

330
00:17:21,200 --> 00:17:22,570
No one told us that before.

331
00:17:22,570 --> 00:17:24,330
I'd better hurry up and find people.

332
00:17:25,190 --> 00:17:27,580
E-Excuse me. Would you like to...

333
00:17:27,580 --> 00:17:31,200
Hm? You reek of baronet stench.

334
00:17:36,500 --> 00:17:37,540
Um...

335
00:17:38,500 --> 00:17:40,610
Yeah, I don't associate with trash.

336
00:17:43,200 --> 00:17:44,750
Trash, huh?

337
00:17:49,080 --> 00:17:50,420
Hey, wanna team up?

338
00:17:51,500 --> 00:17:53,740
Heya, Noir!

339
00:17:53,740 --> 00:17:56,380
E-Emma? What are you doing here?

340
00:17:56,380 --> 00:17:58,240
What about your librarian job?

341
00:17:58,240 --> 00:18:02,430
I quit. I figured I'd give the
Hero Academy a shot, too.

342
00:18:02,430 --> 00:18:05,560
I-I can't believe you quit that easily...

343
00:18:05,560 --> 00:18:07,590
Well, I didn't get to be with you.

344
00:18:07,590 --> 00:18:08,310
Huh?

345
00:18:08,310 --> 00:18:11,940
Noir, you doofus. Come on, let's team up.

346
00:18:13,700 --> 00:18:15,640
Hey, want to team up?

347
00:18:16,650 --> 00:18:18,790
I'm Lenore Bludon.

348
00:18:18,790 --> 00:18:21,490
You don't need to be formal with me.
The more casual, the better.

349
00:18:22,010 --> 00:18:25,390
I'm Emma Brightness, my la... Lenore.

350
00:18:25,390 --> 00:18:29,060
Brightness? Ah, a barony.

351
00:18:29,520 --> 00:18:31,530
I'm Noir Stardia.

352
00:18:31,530 --> 00:18:34,040
I didn't ask for your name.

353
00:18:34,040 --> 00:18:37,570
Why would I bother remembering
the name of a baronet?

354
00:18:37,570 --> 00:18:38,380
Huh?

355
00:18:38,380 --> 00:18:39,580
Now, then...

356
00:18:39,580 --> 00:18:44,110
Gather as many materials
as you can by noon tomorrow.

357
00:18:44,710 --> 00:18:46,630
You can obtain them in any way you'd like.

358
00:18:46,630 --> 00:18:47,770
Begin!

359
00:18:47,770 --> 00:18:48,470
The marketplace!

360
00:18:48,470 --> 00:18:49,640
I'm buying everything!

361
00:18:49,640 --> 00:18:52,910
Y-You can buy the materials, too?

362
00:18:52,910 --> 00:18:56,650
I guess so. He never said you had to
actually defeat any monsters, so...

363
00:18:56,650 --> 00:18:59,400
Let's split up.

364
00:18:59,960 --> 00:19:03,740
Don't drag us down, Mr. Bottom
of the Aristocratic Food Chain.

365
00:19:04,240 --> 00:19:07,350
I guess the rich definitely
have the upper hand.

366
00:19:07,350 --> 00:19:08,320
Yeah...

367
00:19:08,820 --> 00:19:10,700
What are you going to do, Noir?

368
00:19:10,700 --> 00:19:13,630
If you're going to hunt for your
materials, I'll come with you.

369
00:19:13,630 --> 00:19:16,100
No, you wait here, Emma.

370
00:19:16,490 --> 00:19:18,520
I have an idea.

371
00:19:19,720 --> 00:19:22,930
I was sure there'd be plenty of rare
monsters in a hidden dungeon.

372
00:19:22,930 --> 00:19:26,390
And that's why I came to
the third floor, but...

373
00:19:27,600 --> 00:19:29,850
Are you serious right now?!

374
00:19:30,940 --> 00:19:33,370
I'm still level 23...

375
00:19:30,940 --> 00:19:37,690
Dead Reaper Lv.99

376
00:19:30,940 --> 00:19:37,690
Skill [Execution Slash]
Skill Any damage dealt to its enemy with the
Skill Scythe means Instant Death. Effect cannot
Skill be avoided without specific resistance.

377
00:19:33,750 --> 00:19:36,960
Not to mention, if that Scythe hits me,
it's an insta-death for me.

378
00:19:47,360 --> 00:19:51,330
I-If I use my Editor skill and
delete its Instant Death attack...

379
00:19:52,330 --> 00:19:56,790
Skill [Execution Slash]

380
00:19:52,540 --> 00:19:56,790
LP needed to delete: 4000

381
00:19:53,680 --> 00:19:55,880
Nope! I'd literally die eight times!

382
00:19:59,050 --> 00:20:08,010
Noir Stardia

383
00:19:59,600 --> 00:20:01,780
I created the skill Heavy
and Bestowed it on the Reaper.

384
00:20:02,860 --> 00:20:04,900
I managed to stop it for now,

385
00:20:04,900 --> 00:20:07,720
but that instantly cost me 200 LP...

386
00:20:10,350 --> 00:20:12,380
I feel so weak...

387
00:20:13,230 --> 00:20:16,790
I lost so much LP, I can actually
feel my life draining away...

388
00:20:17,230 --> 00:20:19,460
But... I have to do this...

389
00:20:19,460 --> 00:20:20,990
There's no other way!

390
00:20:28,060 --> 00:20:32,500
I'll use 100 LP and my Editor skill to make
the Stone Bullet size 100 centimeters!

391
00:20:28,870 --> 00:20:34,000
Stone Bullet

392
00:20:28,870 --> 00:20:34,000
Noir Stardia

393
00:20:35,420 --> 00:20:38,880
You know, you seem a bit thin.
Have you been eating properly?

394
00:20:38,880 --> 00:20:42,330
Here. This should fill you up!

395
00:20:43,690 --> 00:20:45,390
Stone Bullet 100!

396
00:20:55,980 --> 00:20:58,730
Noir Stardia

397
00:20:56,870 --> 00:20:58,730
I-I'm exhausted...

398
00:21:03,430 --> 00:21:08,490
And now I will announce the top three
teams from the entrance exam results.

399
00:21:08,490 --> 00:21:12,370
He hasn't called our team at all.

400
00:21:12,370 --> 00:21:14,040
Y-Yeah...

401
00:21:14,620 --> 00:21:20,210
In third place, Team Genos with 5,890 points.

402
00:21:21,150 --> 00:21:26,070
In second place, Team Elizabeth
with 11,550 points.

403
00:21:26,070 --> 00:21:28,310
H-He still hasn't called us.

404
00:21:28,830 --> 00:21:30,430
Maybe we didn't even rank...

405
00:21:30,430 --> 00:21:33,280
W-We should be okay.

406
00:21:33,280 --> 00:21:35,060
I mean, Master said...

407
00:21:35,980 --> 00:21:39,520
It wouldn't be weird if I brought
this to the exam, right?

408
00:21:39,520 --> 00:21:40,230
Nah.

409
00:21:40,230 --> 00:21:43,980
It's better than bringing a golden slime,
which doesn't exist on this continent.

410
00:21:43,980 --> 00:21:46,110
They're grunts anyway, so you'll be fine.

411
00:21:46,420 --> 00:21:50,210
B-But... if he doesn't call us...

412
00:21:52,120 --> 00:21:53,840
And in first place...

413
00:21:56,830 --> 00:22:00,460
Team Lenore with 128,000 points!

414
00:22:01,070 --> 00:22:03,630
O-One hundred and twenty...

415
00:22:03,630 --> 00:22:05,090
...eight thousand...

416
00:22:05,090 --> 00:22:09,090
They had the skull of the extremely
diabolical Dead Reaper among their materials.

417
00:22:09,090 --> 00:22:12,340
This means they pass and
rewrite history with that score.

418
00:22:12,340 --> 00:22:16,390
Wh-What were you saying
about this being a grunt, Master?

419
00:22:16,390 --> 00:22:19,290
Whoops, my bad.

420
00:22:19,290 --> 00:22:22,240
A Dead Reaper is nothing to me,

421
00:22:22,240 --> 00:22:25,190
but I guess a student hunting
them would be a miracle.

422
00:22:25,700 --> 00:22:27,500
Well, whatever.

423
00:22:29,200 --> 00:22:33,450
And so, I safely passed the exam
for the Hero Academy.

424
00:22:33,450 --> 00:22:37,460
My family was ecstatic, and this
brightened everyone's moods.

425
00:22:37,840 --> 00:22:40,480
That is, until we saw the enrollment fee.

426
00:22:40,920 --> 00:22:43,160
Three hundred thousand rels?

427
00:22:43,160 --> 00:22:45,960
How am I supposed to get that kind of money?

428
00:24:17,710 --> 00:24:20,270
Next time, "The Guild and the Receptionist."

